data.description: Gorgeous almost brand new home that's available now without the wait. VERY TASTEFULLY done with a wonderfully open layout you'll love! Tray ceiling, gas stove. Nursery or office. Covered back porch. Solid quartz on every surface. Community lake. Trail connects to Yellow Creek Park! High efficiency furnace, step free one level home. $5,000 in custom blinds. Phils Custom Cabinetry, All 9 foot ceilings Large vaulted master bedroom. Seller built new and relocated!
